{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01SJovDJtWUNca99iNdhGDAs","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All 4 infrastructure files have been successfully rewritten from Quarkus to Spring Boot. Here's a summary of what was completed:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\n### 1. LoggerProducer.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/LoggerProducer.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed CDI producer pattern (@ApplicationScoped, @Produces, InjectionPoint)\n- Converted to a simple Spring @Component placeholder\n- Added documentation explaining that Spring uses direct Logger instantiation in each class\n\n### 2. CargoUpdated.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/CargoUpdated.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Removed CDI @Qualifier annotation and related imports\n- Simplified to a marker annotation for backward compatibility\n- Added documentation explaining Spring's ApplicationEventPublisher approach\n\n### 3. ExternalRoutingService.java\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/routing/ExternalRoutingService.java`\n\n**Changes:**\n- Replaced @ApplicationScoped with @Service\n- Replaced @Inject with @Autowired\n- Replaced @ConfigProperty with @Value\n- Replaced JAX-RS Client (WebTarget) with Spring RestTemplate\n- Removed @PostConstruct initialization (no longer needed)\n- Changed Logger injection to static field instantiation\n- Updated fetchRoutesForSpecification() to use RestTemplate.getForObject()\n\n### 4. JmsConfig.java (NEW FILE)\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsConfig.java`\n\n**Created:**\n- New Spring Configuration class with @EnableJms\n- Configured JmsListenerContainerFactory for message listeners\n- Configured Jackson JSON message converter for JMS\n- Configured JmsTemplate for sending messages\n\nAll files have been successfully converted from Quarkus/CDI patterns to Spring Boot equivalents while maintaining the same functionality."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"b5abb741-a624-42c4-8aae-ecb1622fdde2"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_013miDQQ4H2WRCwFNJuH1WVr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All 4 JPA repository files have been successfully rewritten from Quarkus Panache to Spring Data JPA/EntityManager style. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\nAll 4 repository files have been successfully converted from Quarkus Panache to Spring Data JPA/EntityManager style:\n\n### 1. JpaCargoRepository.java\n**Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java`\n\n**Key Changes**:\n- Removed `PanacheRepositoryBase<Cargo, Long>` interface\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Replaced `@Inject Event<Cargo>` with `@Autowired ApplicationEventPublisher`\n- Added `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Converted Panache `find()` method to `entityManager.createNamedQuery()`\n- Changed `persist()` to `entityManager.merge()` in the store method\n- Changed `cargoUpdated.fireAsync()` to `eventPublisher.publishEvent()`\n- Added `listAll()` method using JPQL query\n\n### 2. JpaHandlingEventRepository.java\n**Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaHandlingEventRepository.java`\n\n**Key Changes**:\n- Removed `PanacheRepositoryBase<HandlingEvent, Long>` interface\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Added `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Changed `persist(event)` to `entityManager.persist(event)`\n- Converted Panache named query to `entityManager.createNamedQuery()`\n\n### 3. JpaLocationRepository.java\n**Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaLocationRepository.java`\n\n**Key Changes**:\n- Removed `PanacheRepositoryBase<Location, Long>` interface\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Added `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Converted Panache named query to `entityManager.createNamedQuery()`\n- Added `listAll()` method using JPQL query\n\n### 4. JpaVoyageRepository.java\n**Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaVoyageRepository.java`\n\n**Key Changes**:\n- Removed `PanacheRepositoryBase<Voyage, Long>` interface\n- Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Repository`\n- Added `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Converted Panache named query to `entityManager.createNamedQuery()`\n- Added `listAll()` method using JPQL query with ORDER BY clause\n\nAll repositories now use standard Spring annotations and EntityManager for database operations, maintaining compatibility with the named queries defined on the JPA entities."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"f092cd48-9894-434e-bc94-4c4d926b88d0"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01Us5MLUNzAEN5mswTRuYLzw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01NhDkB1cf29kGL1PJQBDyxT","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.logging.Level;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.ApplicationEvents;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.Cargo;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.handling.HandlingEvent;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.handling.HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;\nimport org.springframework.jms.core.JmsTemplate;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\n\n@Service\npublic class JmsApplicationEvents implements ApplicationEvents, Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n  private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(JmsApplicationEvents.class.getName());\n\n  @Autowired\n  private JmsTemplate jmsTemplate;\n\n  @Value(\"${app.jms.CargoHandledQueue}\")\n  private String cargoHandledQueue;\n\n  @Value(\"${app.jms.MisdirectedCargoQueue}\")\n  private String misdirectedCargoQueue;\n\n  @Value(\"${app.jms.DeliveredCargoQueue}\")\n  private String deliveredCargoQueue;\n\n  @Value(\"${app.jms.HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptQueue}\")\n  private String handlingEventQueue;\n\n  @Override\n  public void cargoWasHandled(HandlingEvent event) {\n    Cargo cargo = event.getCargo();\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo was handled {0}\", cargo);\n    jmsTemplate.convertAndSend(cargoHandledQueue, cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString());\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void cargoWasMisdirected(Cargo cargo) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo was misdirected {0}\", cargo);\n    jmsTemplate.convertAndSend(misdirectedCargoQueue, cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString());\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void cargoHasArrived(Cargo cargo) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Cargo has arrived {0}\", cargo);\n    jmsTemplate.convertAndSend(deliveredCargoQueue, cargo.getTrackingId().getIdString());\n  }\n\n  @Override\n  public void receivedHandlingEventRegistrationAttempt(HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt attempt) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Received handling event registration attempt {0}\", attempt);\n    jmsTemplate.convertAndSend(handlingEventQueue, attempt);\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6695,"cache_read_input_tokens":18281,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6695,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2704},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Q4SrzbxcRnV97SCwLhGoUW","session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"1ac556bf-8578-476b-a9b5-cfa800442693"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01Us5MLUNzAEN5mswTRuYLzw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01ApUAizyGsA5diK6yWhNRM4","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n\nimport java.util.logging.Level;\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.CargoInspectionService;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain.model.cargo.TrackingId;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.jms.annotation.JmsListener;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Component\npublic class CargoHandledConsumer {\n\n  private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(CargoHandledConsumer.class.getName());\n\n  @Autowired\n  private CargoInspectionService cargoInspectionService;\n\n  @JmsListener(destination = \"${app.jms.CargoHandledQueue}\")\n  public void onMessage(String trackingIdString) {\n    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"CargoHandledConsumer received: {0}\", trackingIdString);\n    cargoInspectionService.inspectCargo(new TrackingId(trackingIdString));\n  }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6695,"cache_read_input_tokens":18281,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6695,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2704},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Q4SrzbxcRnV97SCwLhGoUW","session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"aa225056-7873-404f-9b68-f6cd8b299df7"}
