{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WwrnmtX9Ro8ruTLD8A1bME","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.messaging.jms;\n     2→\n     3→import java.util.logging.Level;\n     4→import java.util.logging.Logger;\n     5→import org.springframework.jms.annotation.JmsListener;\n     6→import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n     7→\n     8→@Component\n     9→public class RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer {\n    10→\n    11→  private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.class.getName());\n    12→\n    13→  @JmsListener(destination = \"${app.jms.RejectedRegistrationAttemptsQueue}\")\n    14→  public void onMessage(String trackingIdString) {\n    15→    logger.log(Level.INFO, \"Rejected registration attempt of cargo with tracking ID {0}.\", trackingIdString);\n    16→  }\n    17→}\n    18→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Q4SrzbxcRnV97SCwLhGoUW","session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"8f03708f-dbd1-4667-ac24-a4059da8f876"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Q4SrzbxcRnV97SCwLhGoUW","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully converted all 6 JMS messaging files from Quarkus to Spring Boot. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Files Successfully Converted\n\nAll 6 files have been rewritten with Spring Boot annotations and patterns:\n\n### 1. JmsApplicationEvents.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/JmsApplicationEvents.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service`\n- `@Inject ConnectionFactory` → `@Autowired JmsTemplate`\n- `@ConfigProperty` → `@Value`\n- Removed manual JMSContext creation and replaced with `JmsTemplate.convertAndSend()`\n- Removed `@Inject Logger` and used static logger initialization\n\n### 2. CargoHandledConsumer.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/CargoHandledConsumer.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n- `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- Removed `Runnable` implementation and manual consumer setup\n- `@Observes StartupEvent/ShutdownEvent` → Removed (not needed with `@JmsListener`)\n- Added `@JmsListener` annotation for declarative message consumption\n- Simplified from manual JMS consumer loop to annotation-driven approach\n\n### 3. DeliveredCargoConsumer.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/DeliveredCargoConsumer.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n- Added `@JmsListener` for declarative message consumption\n- Removed manual ExecutorService, Runnable implementation, and lifecycle management\n\n### 4. MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- Same pattern as DeliveredCargoConsumer\n- Simplified from manual JMS consumer to `@JmsListener` annotation\n\n### 5. HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n- `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- Added `@JmsListener` for ObjectMessage consumption\n- Changed error handling to log instead of throwing RuntimeException\n\n### 6. RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java\n**Location:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java`\n\n**Key Changes:**\n- Same pattern as other consumers\n- Simplified from manual JMS consumer to `@JmsListener` annotation\n\n## Summary of Replacements Applied\n\n1. **Annotations:**\n   - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service` (for JmsApplicationEvents) or `@Component` (for consumers)\n   - `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n   - `@ConfigProperty(name = \"...\")` → `@Value(\"${...}\")`\n   - Added `@JmsListener(destination = \"...\")` for message consumers\n\n2. **Imports:**\n   - `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` → `org.springframework.stereotype.Service/Component`\n   - `jakarta.inject.Inject` → `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n   - `org.eclipse.microprofile.config.inject.ConfigProperty` → `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value`\n   - Removed `io.quarkus.runtime.*` imports\n   - Added `org.springframework.jms.annotation.JmsListener` and `org.springframework.jms.core.JmsTemplate`\n\n3. **Architecture Changes:**\n   - Replaced manual JMS ConnectionFactory + JMSContext usage with Spring's `JmsTemplate`\n   - Replaced manual message consumers (Runnable with ExecutorService) with `@JmsListener` annotations\n   - Removed lifecycle event handling (`@Observes StartupEvent/ShutdownEvent`) as Spring Boot manages this automatically\n   - Simplified message sending with `jmsTemplate.convertAndSend()`\n\nAll files have been successfully converted and are ready for use in a Spring Boot application."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"d02bbd6d-7781-431f-9fbe-f8d41bf61daa"}
