{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014HJ8s7zCNtVZZMvamQGHCX","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! The HandlingReport.java file already exists. Now let me create a comprehensive summary of all the changes made:\n\n## Summary: Interfaces Layer Conversion from Quarkus/JSF to Spring Boot\n\nI have successfully rewritten the interfaces layer from Quarkus/JSF to Spring Boot. Here's a detailed breakdown of all the files that were converted:\n\n### Files Successfully Converted:\n\n#### 1. **HandlingReportService.java**\n   - **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/rest/HandlingReportService.java`\n   - **Changes**:\n     - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@RestController`\n     - Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired`\n     - Replaced `@Path(\"/handling\")` with `@RequestMapping(\"/rest/handling\")`\n     - Replaced `@POST` with `@PostMapping(\"/reports\")`\n     - Removed `@Consumes` annotation (Spring handles this automatically)\n     - Added `@RequestBody` annotation for request parameter\n     - Changed return type from `void` to `ResponseEntity<Void>`\n     - Replaced Jakarta transaction with Spring `@Transactional`\n\n#### 2. **GraphTraversalService.java**\n   - **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/api/GraphTraversalService.java`\n   - **Changes**:\n     - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@RestController`\n     - Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired`\n     - Replaced `@Path(\"/graph-traversal\")` with `@RequestMapping(\"/rest/graph-traversal\")`\n     - Replaced `@GET` with `@GetMapping(\"/shortest-path\")`\n     - Replaced `@QueryParam` with `@RequestParam`\n     - Added `required = false` for optional deadline parameter\n     - Removed `@Produces` annotation (Spring handles content negotiation)\n     - Removed `@Transactional` (not needed for this read-only service)\n\n#### 3. **GraphDao.java**\n   - **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/internal/GraphDao.java`\n   - **Changes**:\n     - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n     - This is a simple DAO component used by GraphTraversalService\n\n#### 4. **RealtimeCargoTrackingService.java**\n   - **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/sse/RealtimeCargoTrackingService.java`\n   - **Changes**:\n     - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@RestController`\n     - Replaced `@Path(\"/cargo\")` with `@RequestMapping(\"/rest/cargo\")`\n     - Replaced JAX-RS SSE (`Sse`, `SseBroadcaster`, `SseEventSink`) with Spring's `SseEmitter`\n     - Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired`\n     - Replaced `@ObservesAsync @CargoUpdated` with `@EventListener`\n     - Removed `@PostConstruct` and `@PreDestroy` lifecycle methods (replaced with emitter callbacks)\n     - Changed from push-based broadcaster to pull-based emitter list management\n     - Added error handling for initial SSE data transmission\n\n#### 5. **DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java**\n   - **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/DefaultBookingServiceFacade.java`\n   - **Changes**:\n     - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n     - Replaced all `@Inject` with `@Autowired` (8 dependencies)\n     - No other logic changes required\n\n### Assembler Classes Converted:\n\nAll assembler classes in `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/`:\n\n#### 6. **CargoRouteDtoAssembler.java**\n   - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n   - Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired`\n\n#### 7. **CargoStatusDtoAssembler.java**\n   - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n   - Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired`\n\n#### 8. **LocationDtoAssembler.java**\n   - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n   - No dependency injection required\n\n#### 9. **TrackingEventsDtoAssembler.java**\n   - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n   - No dependency injection required\n\n#### 10. **ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler.java**\n   - Replaced `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n   - Replaced `@Inject` with `@Autowired`\n\n### Key Conversion Patterns Applied:\n\n1. **Dependency Injection**: CDI (`@Inject`) → Spring (`@Autowired`)\n2. **Component Stereotypes**: \n   - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component` (for utilities/DAOs)\n   - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service` (for business facades)\n   - `@ApplicationScoped` → `@RestController` (for REST endpoints)\n3. **REST Annotations**:\n   - JAX-RS (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`, `@QueryParam`) → Spring MVC (`@RequestMapping`, `@GetMapping`, `@PostMapping`, `@RequestParam`, `@RequestBody`)\n4. **Transaction Management**: Jakarta `@Transactional` → Spring `@Transactional`\n5. **Server-Sent Events**: JAX-RS SSE API → Spring `SseEmitter`\n6. **Event Handling**: CDI `@ObservesAsync` → Spring `@EventListener`\n\n### REST Endpoints Now Available:\n\n1. `POST /rest/handling/reports` - Submit handling events\n2. `GET /rest/graph-traversal/shortest-path` - Find routes between locations\n3. `GET /rest/cargo` (SSE) - Real-time cargo tracking stream\n\nAll files have been successfully written and the interfaces layer is now fully compatible with Spring Boot, replacing the Quarkus/JSF implementation with Spring MVC REST controllers and Spring's SSE support."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"943fd8a3-59da-4c74-aa18-45ac641a0f61"}
