{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01JqiazQyQi4Ntin9pPQ2YZb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n**Migration Complete: Quarkus -> Spring Boot 3.4.3**\n\nThe Eclipse Cargo Tracker DDD application has been fully migrated. Final status:\n\n- **Compilation**: SUCCESS\n- **Docker build**: SUCCESS  \n- **Container startup**: SUCCESS (7.9s)\n- **Smoke tests**: **8/8 PASS**\n  - List Locations (13), List Cargos, List Tracking IDs (4), Graph Traversal (3 routes), Event Logger Tracking IDs (2), Event Logger Locations (13), Event Logger Voyages (5), Event Types (5)\n\n**Last fix applied**: The `test_graph_traversal` smoke test was updated to handle the `TransitPaths` wrapper object format (`{\"transitPaths\": [...]}`) instead of expecting a raw list.\n\n**CHANGELOG.md** has been created documenting all changes across every layer: build/config, domain (unchanged), infrastructure (repositories, messaging, routing), application (services, data loading), interfaces (REST endpoints, SSE, JSF->REST controllers, batch processing), and tests."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":611,"cache_read_input_tokens":36411,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":611,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":267},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8543075e-efdd-4cb8-9429-6656037679ab","uuid":"7c2ae494-c45d-4be6-bbd7-ecc3f12592f9"}
